- Job security?

761
00:45:22.507 --> 00:45:24.505
- (SHUTS DOOR)
- Who knew?

762
00:45:24.506 --> 00:45:27.505
So, you're right.
Hemmerling came through.

763
00:45:27.505 --> 00:45:29.508
- Yeah, 'cause of the angel.
- Aw, whatever.

764
00:45:29.509 --> 00:45:33.501
- No, we got angels helping the team.
- Ah, well, that may be,

765
00:45:33.501 --> 00:45:34.504
but we're winning.

766
00:45:34.507 --> 00:45:35.507
Yeah.

767
00:45:35.509 --> 00:45:38.504
All the games, man!
Can you believe it?

768
00:45:38.509 --> 00:45:41.505
