for us to talk on the phone.

770
00:45:44.501 --> 00:45:46.509
You mean, the phone in the dugout
you're always yelling into...

771
00:45:47.500 --> 00:45:48.509
and-and banging against
the wall and spitting at?

772
00:45:48.509 --> 00:45:50.504
Yeah, yeah, yeah, that phone.

773
00:45:50.504 --> 00:45:52.506
Cool! (LAUGHS)

