780
00:46:10.506 --> 00:46:12.503
He used to live
in a car with his mom.

781
00:46:13.500 --> 00:46:15.507
He slept in the front seat
all curled up like a cat or something.

782
00:46:15.509 --> 00:46:18.503
When he gets in a car,
his stomachache comes back.

783
00:46:21.500 --> 00:46:23.503
(BUS HONKS)

784
00:46:34.500 --> 00:46:35.503
(OPENS DOOR)

785
00:46:39.502 --> 00:46:40.509
- I'll call you tomorrow.
- All right.

786
00:46:42.501 --> 00:46:45.501
- Thank you for the ride home.
- He speaks?

787
00:46:47.500 --> 00:46:48.409
(CLOSES DOOR)

788
00:46:48.507 --> 00:46:50.507
- Hi. You guys have a good time?
- Hi.

789
00:46:51.501 --> 00:46:52.507
- A blast!
- We won!

790
00:46:52.507 --> 00:46:55.500
- Great.
- Where's Miguel?

791
00:46:55.504 --> 00:46:56.508
I got him all sorts of stuff.

792
00:46:57.509 --> 00:47:00.506
Miguel got placed in a foster home
this afternoon.

793
00:47:02.502 --> 00:47:04.505
- He got placed?
- Miguel's gone?

794
00:47:04.506 --> 00:47:05.506
Mmm-hmm.

795
00:47:06.507 --> 00:47:08.503
Where? With who?

796
00:47:09.500 --> 00:47:11.501
A real nice family
from Northridge.

797
00:47:11.504 --> 00:47:14.509
I'm gonna miss him.
I really liked Miguel!

798
00:47:17.505 --> 00:47:19.509
I only have a licence
for short-term care.

799
00:47:20.501 --> 00:47:22.507
You know? M-Miguel's been here
for, what, six months?

800
00:47:22.509 --> 00:47:24.509
- I think seven.
- Seven months. Right.

801
00:47:25.509 --> 00:47:30.500
That's what happens, you know?
I mean, you understand that, Roger.

802
00:47:30.505 --> 00:47:32.503
Oh, don't feel bad, Maggie.

803
00:47:34.502 --> 00:47:36.507
I bet we see him again.
Maybe in court or something.

804
00:47:37.506 --> 00:47:39.502
Oh, Roger.

805
00:47:40.507 --> 00:47:42.501
God forbid.

806
00:47:45.508 --> 00:47:48.507
- JP: Roger?
- ROGER: What?

807
00:47:50.508 --> 00:47:52.502
Are you asleep?

808
00:47:53.505 --> 00:47:55.506
If I was asleep,
how'd I be talkin' to you?

809
00:47:56.508 --> 00:47:58.507
You could be "sleeptalking."

