00:51:51.503 --> 00:51:53.507
- You talkin' to me?
- Yeah.

853
00:51:54.508 --> 00:51:56.504
So get your stuff together.

854
00:52:02.504 --> 00:52:05.505
RANCH: Starting pitcher announced
for this game was Dan Prince...

855
00:52:05.506 --> 00:52:08.507
but just moments ago,
the Angels made a dramatic change...

856
00:52:08.508 --> 00:52:11.508
and activated the
long-injured Mel Clark.

857
00:52:12.500 --> 00:52:14.508
League rules specify that up
until the first pitch is thrown,

858
00:52:14.508 --> 00:52:16.502
