nervous out there.

872
00:53:03.508 --> 00:53:06.501
RANCH: Not as nervous
as George Knox.

873
00:53:24.506 --> 00:53:26.500
RANCH: Clark takes the sign.

874
00:53:31.503 --> 00:53:32.509
Talk about heat!

875
00:53:32.509 --> 00:53:33.509
- Messmer felt that one.
