00:53:59.500 --> 00:54:00.502
Mel!

887
00:54:00.507 --> 00:54:02.502
Way to go!

888
00:54:02.508 --> 00:54:04.500
All right, Mel!

889
00:54:04.507 --> 00:54:05.704
(GRUNTING)

